00:46:04,362 --> 00:46:05,695
(Crashing)

756
00:46:11,895 --> 00:46:25,962
*

757
00:46:25,995 --> 00:46:28,562
Help me, God!

758
00:46:28,595 --> 00:46:30,995
Ahh!

759
00:46:40,329 --> 00:46:42,262
Ugh!

