791
00:49:46,795 --> 00:49:47,862
TARAS:
I can't see him.

792
00:49:47,895 --> 00:49:50,729
Where is he?

793
00:49:50,762 --> 00:49:52,495
He's under the table.

794
00:49:56,562 --> 00:49:59,662
My ears must be clogged.

795
00:49:59,695 --> 00:50:02,562
He kicked my head!

796
00:50:02,595 --> 00:50:04,562
